g \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. Cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 trung th\u1ef1c, l\u00f2ng tr\u1eafc \u1ea9n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec c\u00e1c m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc \\\"Open Secret\\\", h\u00e3y chia s\u1ebb suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ho\u1eb7c tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp.\\n```\\n    \\n    B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n nh\u00e1p n\u00e0y th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?  \\n    - N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tinh ch\u1ec9nh, b\u1ed5 sung ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda chi ti\u1ebft.  \\n    - N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh **xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n** ngay.\\n\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\":\"adk-8b6351d5-9a18-4312-9f7b-b342c51ec478\",\"args\":{\"agent_name\":\"writing_pipeline\"},\"name\":\"transfer_to_agent\"},{\"id\":\"adk-51b25700-8e0e-42f2-a06d-5b47c42a8601\",\"args\":{},\"name\":\"exit_loop\"},{\"id\":\"adk-17c2d19f-a1d3-45df-bf8e-5a53b60f66d4\",\"args\":{},\"name\":\"save_draft_content\"}],\"tool_responses\":[],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":0.0},\"eval_metric_results\":[{\"metric_name\":\"tool_trajectory_avg_score\",\"threshold\":1.0,\"judge_model_options\":null,\"score\":1.0,\"eval_status\":1},{\"metric_name\":\"response_match_score\",\"threshold\":0.3,\"judge_model_opti